reviewText: My son absolutely loves most all hooplkidz. While we didn't mind this disc it absolutely could have been better. Anny, Ben and Mango should be in all the videos as  it says they are in the description. I wish more popular Christmas sons were on here.
Unfortunately the CD was not fixed well in the box. It was moving inside and as a result it was scratched all over. The video and the music go but their quality leaves a lot to be desired.
